ExtraInfo.Rem: BrainWave Generator is a brain stimulation application that works by generating binaural beat frequencies. With binaural beats, you can stimulate your brain to make yourself relaxed, help in meditation or self-hypnosis, enhance learning capabilities, induce sleep, help focusing attention, and so on.
